# LEC Match Predictor

> Predict the winner of professional League of Legends LEC matches using machine learning, using only **pre-game** data to avoid data leakage.

## 🧠 Project Goal

Most esports prediction models accidentally use in-game stats (gold diff, kill diff) that aren't known before a match starts. This project builds a **fair predictor** that only uses information available before the first minion spawns:

- Team recent win rates (last 5 games)
- Head-to-head historical record
- Draft composition features (planned for v2)
- Tournament stage / playoff pressure

## 🏆 Current Performance

| Model              | Accuracy | Precision | Recall | F1   |
|-------------------|----------|-----------|--------|------|
| Logistic Regression | 0.62     | 0.61      | 0.62   | 0.61 |
| Random Forest       | 0.67     | 0.66      | 0.67   | 0.66 |
| **CatBoost**        | **0.71** | **0.70**  | **0.71** | **0.70** |

*Baseline (always pick Fnatic): 0.53*

